titles.title: Authorizing the Clerk to inform the President of the election of the Clerk.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

bill.summary: 2/15/2007--Passed House without amendment. (This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary of that version is repeated here.) Instructs the Clerk to inform the President of the United States that the House of Representatives has elected that Lorraine C. Miller, a citizen of Texas, Clerk of the House of Representatives.
